# Payroll Automation System API

A production-oriented REST API built with Django and Django REST Framework for automating payroll processing, employee management, and salary payments.

The project demonstrates modern backend engineering practices including JWT authentication, REST API development, PostgreSQL integration, payment gateway integration, Docker containerization, production deployment, and API documentation.

